<p>In <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_neural_network" t=
itle=3D"Artificial neural network">artificial neural networks</a>, each neu=
ron forms a weighted sum of its inputs and passes the resulting scalar valu=
e through a function referred to as an activation function or transfer func=
tion. If a neuron has n inputs <span class=3D"mwe-math-element"><span class=
