<h2><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Classification_of_activation_function=
s">Classification of activation functions</span><span class=3D"mw-editsecti=
on"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wi=
kipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DActivation_function&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;s=
ection=3D1" title=3D"Edit section: Classification of activation functions">=
edit</a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>The most common activation functions can be divided in three categories:=
 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ridge_function" title=3D"Ridge fu=
nction">ridge functions</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radia=
l_function" title=3D"Radial function">radial functions</a> and <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fold_function" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"=
Fold function">fold functions</a>.
</p>
