ivation functions</span><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-ed=
itsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?=
title=3DActivation_function&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D2" title=3D"Edi=
t section: Ridge activation functions">edit</a><span class=3D"mw-editsectio=
